code: export default function getCookie(name){const nameEQ=name+'=';if(typeof document=='undefined')return null;const ca=document.cookie.split(';');for(let i=0;i<ca.length;i++){let c=ca[i];while(c.charAt(0)===' ')c=c.substring(1,c.length);if(c.indexOf(nameEQ)===0)return c.substring(nameEQ.length,c.length);}return null;}
